OL,3,CGloria Hunniford says death of husband
OL,4,Cwill leave 'enormous void'
OL,6,FGloria Hunniford has announced the
OL,7,Fdeath of her husband of more than 20
OL,8,Fyears, Stephen Way.
OL,10,FThe veteran broadcaster, 84, wed the
OL,11,Fbusinessman in 1998, and she said he
OL,12,Fwould leave "the most enormous void,
OL,13,Fnot only in my life".
OL,15,FIn a statement on Wednesday, his
OL,16,Ffamily said: "It is with huge sadness
OL,17,Fand very heavy hearts that we share
OL,18,Fthe passing of Stephen Way, Gloria's
OL,19,Fbeloved husband, who lost his battle
OL,20,Fyesterday afternoon.
