OL,6,F"Stephen had been heroically fighting
OL,7,Fhis illness... but always with great
OL,8,Ftenacity and a positive spirit."
OL,10,FMr Way was 85, Hunniford's agent
OL,11,Fconfirmed.
OL,13,FHunniford said: "Stephen was a
OL,14,Fgentleman and a giant of a man, who
OL,15,Fwill leave the most enormous void not
OL,16,Fonly in my life, but our entire family.
OL,18,F"He was an incredibly kind, generous,
OL,19,Fand caring man, with a delightfully
OL,20,Fquirky sense of humour, which remained
OL,21,Ftill the end.
