OL,3,CGloria Hunniford says death of husband
OL,4,Cwill leave 'enormous void'
OL,6,F"We had a tremendously happy 25-year
OL,7,Fmarriage and did so many beautiful and
OL,8,Fexciting things together that I will
OL,9,Falways cherish."
OL,11,FMr Way was described as a "wonderful
OL,12,Fhusband, father and grandfather" and
OL,13,FHunniford added: "It's a great shock
OL,14,Fand words cannot express my sadness at
OL,15,Fthis time.
OL,17,F"A bright shining light has dimmed,
OL,18,Fand he shall be missed at every turn."
