OL,7,Fthe death of her former husband Don
OL,8,FKeating as she came off stage after
OL,9,Fhosting a TV chat show in 1997, she
OL,10,Frevealed that year.
OL,12,FNorthern Irish broadcaster Eamonn
OL,13,FHolmes, who got his break when he got
OL,14,FHunniford's job at Good Evening
OL,15,FUlster, also paid tribute.
OL,17,FHe wrote on Instagram: "I feel the
OL,18,Fpain of Gloria my dear friend of 40
OL,19,Fplus years on the loss of Stephen ` a
OL,20,Ftrue gent and a scholar. My genuine
OL,21,Fheartfelt condolences."
