OL,6,FHunniford's daughter Caron Keating,
OL,7,Falso a TV presenter, died after a
OL,8,Fbattle with breast cancer in 2004, and
OL,9,Fshe set up a foundation in her memory.
OL,11,FThe Caron Keating Foundation
OL,12,Ffundraises for cancer charities, as
OL,13,Fwell as raising awareness.
OL,15,FIn 2017, Hunniford became an OBE in
OL,16,Fthe Queen's Birthday Honours for her
OL,17,Fcontribution to cancer charities
OL,18,Fthrough breast screening services and
OL,19,Fcancer support.
